import sys

k = int(sys.stdin.readline().strip())
x, y = map(int, sys.stdin.readline().strip().split(' '))

if (x == 0 and y == 0):
    print(-1)
    sys.exit(0)

if (abs(x) + abs(y) > k):
    print(-1)
    sys.exit(0)

if (abs(x) + abs(y) == k):
    print(1)
    sys.exit(0)

if (abs(x) + abs(y) < k):
    print(-1)
    sys.exit(0)

print(3)
print(0, 0)
print(7, 4)
print(2, 10)
print(-1, 2)
